(Rolling Stone)  -- In the new issue of Rolling Stone -- on stands and online in the digital archives on February 18 (subscription required) -- Justin Bieber takes Rolling Stone contributing editor Vanessa Grigoriadis for a spin around Atlanta in his Range Rover.

Along the way they discuss girls, politics, music, Will Ferrell movies -- and sex.

