Bieber's voice began to change on his last tour.

He's now working with a vocal coach, which involves doing 20 push-ups before before a session to warm up his chest.

"He's got a nice tone to his voice now," says his vocal coach Jan Smith. "It's a good texture, but it doesn't sound like what his fans think he sounds like. He'll get four octaves eventually. He's still young."

